Xtento_GridActions

-------------
  CHANGELOG
-------------

===== 1.0.0 =====
 * Initial Release

[...]

===== 1.2.1 =====
 * Rewrote processor model
 * Suppressed error that could show up for not correctly removed/uninstalled shipping methods

===== 1.2.2 =====
 * Unhold order before invoicing/shipping/completing it.

===== 1.2.3 =====
 * Added example to config.xml to show how the modules columns can be moved to the last columns of the grid.

===== 1.2.4 =====
 * Added a couple new actions to (re-)send emails for already created invoices/shipments.

===== 1.2.5 =====
 * Bugfix release

===== 1.2.6 =====
 * Fixed bug in JS that handles grid carriers/tracking numbers

===== 1.2.7 =====
 * Compatibility with Advanced Order Status

===== 1.2.8 =====
 * Compatibility with certain Amasty extensions

===== 1.2.9 =====
 * Updated XtCore
 * Configuration section opened by default
 * Fixed a bug with regards to status changes

===== 1.3.0 =====
 * Fixed a bug that did not count emails resent as order updates

===== 1.3.1 =====
 * Enhanced EE 1.12 compatibility (Rewrite must be enabled in config.xml)

===== 1.4.0 =====
 + Added permissions to ACL so roles can be limited to allow certain operations only

===== 1.5.0 =====
 * Added ability to render carrier/tracking field into one column in the Sales > Order grid

===== 1.6.0 =====
 + Added ability to mass-capture payments for already invoiced orders
 * Several bugfixes

===== 1.6.1 =====
 * Adjusted adminhtml controller to cope with full page caches better

===== 1.6.2 =====
 + Added option to force order status changes

===== 1.6.3 =====
 + Improved compatibility with not properly uninstalled shipping methods